ctx: apply factorial_cancel with (n := expo n p).
exceptions.exn: In environment factorial_cancel : forall n a b : nat, fact n * a = fact n * b -> a = b p : nat Hp : p <> 0 n, a, b : nat H : expo n p * a = expo n p * b Unable to unify "expo n p * a = expo n p * b" with "fact (expo n p) * a = fact (expo n p) * b".

original: intros H. apply factorial_cancel with (n := expo n p). apply H.
